                    <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button" onclick="q()">请假 &raquo;</a></p>
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img class="rounded-circle" src="@ViewBag.img " alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
<h2>@ViewBag.name</h2>


                <p></p>
                    @*<p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>*@
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img class="rounded-circle" src="~/Image/icon4.gif" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
                    <h2>修改个人资料</h2>
                    <p>Donec sed odio dui. Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.</p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button" onclick="qqq()">修改 &raquo;</a></p>
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
            </div><!-- /.row -->
            <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->
            <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->
        </div><!-- /.container -->
